{
  "stem": "21008.2",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There's a story I really should tell you about that.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they-- they didn't renew the lease.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So we had to move.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "By April of '39 we had to move out.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, it wasn't renewed.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It was-- in the development was a little Catholic church, of course.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And on Saturdays when there was a wedding, the bells would ring.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And the children and even myself, being a little girl, would run there to see the bride.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I was standing there one day and watching or waiting for the bride to come, when a priest came out of the church and chased me away.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "You, Jew, leave, he said to me.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "A priest, in his-- is his robe, or whatever you want to call this.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Yeah, chased me away.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "That-- by the by, I never set foot on that ground again, you know.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I was a little girl.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "My god, I could have been seven, eight, the most.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Because once I went to the Jewish school, I wouldn't even go there, you know.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But I was a little girl.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I know I wore play-- a little play pants-- pants.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I remember how I was dressed when I was chased away from there.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "That was a shock to me that the priest chased me away.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Hm.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Anyhow, we were now talking about--",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Having to move.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And at that time, Jews could not move where they wanted to move.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They had to contact the so-called Reichsvereinigung, which was an administration consisting of Jews by set-- but set up by the Gestapo.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So you had to go to the Reichsvereinigung, you know.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We have-- we need a place to stay.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
